# rune-managed: materialized by `rune sync` from the source-of-truth
# registry (nomograph/runes). Tracking the synced copy creates a drift
# class where every rune update produces a "sync" commit on this repo,
# and the committed copy can fall behind the registry between syncs.
# `.claude/rune.lock` (when present) pins which registry version each
# skill came from.
.claude/skills/
.agent/skills
